rows.label: tlk45310111_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Apparently the Maelstrom isn't going
to be setting sail any time soon.

rows.label: tlk45310111_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Normally I'd gather up a crew, take
this ship out to a distant quadrant and
try to haul up some big prize.

rows.label: tlk45310111_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But I guess it's not so bad to go out
salvaging on my own once in a while.

rows.label: tlk45310111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Takes me back to simpler days when
I'd go out, collect a bunch of treasures
and be thrilled at every G I earned!
